data.description: Welcome to this unique investment opportunity perfectly suited for Airbnb enthusiasts and savvy investors. Nestled in a prime location, this three bedroom, two bathroom offers not just a home, but an exceptional income-generating prospect. With its thoughtful design, desirable amenities, and proximity to Elephant Butte Lake State Park, Sierra Del Rio Golf Course and the T or C Hot Springs, this remodeled Home is a standout choice for the flourishing short-term rental market or to just call Home. The Home is also available completely furnished including all housewares to put on Airbnb the weekend after closing for $275,000.
